{"tid":1202969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港爆了!!!] 高銀因應近日社會矛盾棄標啟德商業地 石禮謙要求開緊急董事會","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:13:30.000Z","uid":10200,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac84b6dfaf92ed52317f9c8ae7d9bdfeca3fbfa","tid":1202969,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"高銀金融發公告指，應獨立非執行董事石禮謙要求，昨日召開緊急董事會會議，連同石禮謙在內，共6名董事認為，近期發生的社會矛盾及經濟不穩定，將可能對香港商業地產市場的增長，產生負面影響，提出暫停向啟德4C區4號商業/酒店用地提供財務資助，有關2500萬元按金將會被政府沒收。<br />\n<br />\n有關議案獲大多數董事投票贊成通過，棄標地皮。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，高銀金融主席潘蘇通並不認同有關董事的看法，又說有信心地皮可與集團已有的4B區4號住宅用地帶來協同效益。<br />\n<br />\n高銀金融上月中，以逾111.2億元投得啟德4C區4號商業/酒店用地，是政府首幅批出的跑道區商業用地，每呎樓面地價近1.29萬元，創東九龍商業用地呎價新高。高銀當時預計，總投資額約160億至180億元。"},{"pid":"9c29b5c6db6212c9acc4f94fef45632cebe8b992","tid":1202969,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462150-20190611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462150-20190611.htm&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo3T1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=e06236b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462150-20190611.htm&h=f2a26241\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462150-20190611.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fecfaa0b654c7a5e75c1c164be77e7496b96609b","tid":1202969,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"撤！"},{"pid":"ed45dea5db194f628bc873cf9c94beb90b1b404a","tid":1202969,"uid":23221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"睇黎獨立戰爭無可避免了"},{"pid":"f23198f7bc456cd64fb95213632de0d6390d8e18","tid":1202969,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"石禮謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass